Movie Ticket Booking System in C
Welcome to the Movie Ticket Booking System repository! This project aims to provide a seamless experience for users to book movie tickets with ease. Below you will find information on how to use the system, its features, and how to contribute.

Features
User Authentication: Users can create new accounts or log in with existing ones.
Movie Booking: Users can browse available movies and book tickets for desired showtimes.
Admin Panel: Administrators can efficiently manage movie viewings, ensuring smooth operation.
File Storage: User and movie information is stored in files for easy access and retrieval.
Error Handling: Robust error handling to ensure a smooth user experience.
